This directory contains a simple framework to implement and test window
based image filters.

video_filter.cpp
	Contains the main programm. Captures images via opencv and supplies
	them to the filter() function.

window_filter.h
	Base class for window based single channel image filters.

conv_filter.h, rank_filter.h, susan_filter.h
	Implementations of the convolution filter, rank filter and susan filter.

